(403696, 'Dyson', 'misuse of office funds and sex discrimination in hiring', 'On Jan. 31, 1990, the House Committee on Standards of Official Conduct dismissed allegations against Dyson for misuse of office funds and sex discrimination in hiring, having previously declined to consider the allegations when they were first lodged due to the proximity to election day in 1988.', '- date: 1990-01-31', 'e, t, h, i, c, s,  , r, e, s, o, l, v, e, d'),
